  <context>
    <background>
      Per r1 ledger entry RB-T070-02 (filed 2026-05-31, fix-by 2026-07-31): identical pattern to RB-T050-01 (task 034). `CapabilityChangePayload`
      is an `internal sealed record` with optional `int? RetryAfterSeconds = null` (line ~311). The default `System.Text.Json` writer policy
      emits `"retryAfterSeconds": null` for null values; the test asserts omission.

      Frontend defensive null-check (`if (event.data.retryAfterSeconds)`) makes the bug observable only in the wire format. Production correctness
      is preserved end-to-end. Fix is a single attribute addition.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="029" status="must-be-complete">Phase 2 exit triple-run validation before Phase 3 starts</dependency>
    </dependencies>
  </context>

  <relevant-files>
    <file>src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Api/Ai/R2SseEventEmitter.cs</file>
    <file>tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Api/Ai/R2SseEventEmitterTests.cs</file>
    <file>projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md</file>
  </relevant-files>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load r1 ledger entry RB-T070-02 (lines ~523-548) for documented bug + recommended fix.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Api/Ai/R2SseEventEmitter.cs` focusing on `CapabilityChangePayload` (~line 308 record declaration; `RetryAfterSeconds` at ~line 311).</step>
    <step order="3">Add `[property: JsonIgnore(Condition = JsonIgnoreCondition.WhenWritingNull)]` to the `RetryAfterSeconds` record parameter. Ensure `using System.Text.Json.Serialization;` present.</step>
    <step order="4">Build BFF: `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/`. Zero new warnings.</step>
    <step order="5">Edit `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Api/Ai/R2SseEventEmitterTests.cs`: remove `Skip = "..."` on `EmitCapabilityChangeAsync_OmitsRetryAfterSecondsWhenNull` (~line 270); remove per-test `[Trait("status","real-bug-pending-fix")]` override.</step>
    <step order="6">Run targeted tests: `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/ --filter "FullyQualifiedName~R2SseEventEmitterTests"`. Re-enabled test must pass.</step>
    <step order="7">Update ledger row RB-T070-02: status → `repaired`, fix-commit SHA placeholder + today's date.</step>
    <step order="8">Commit: `fix(bff-api): omit null RetryAfterSeconds in CapabilityChangePayload (RB-T070-02; repaired)` per NFR-04.</step>
    <step order="9">Update `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/current-task.md` with completion + commit SHA.</step>
  </steps>

